Docs.summary: If set to 1 this causes events on this calendar to be duplicated with Events#LAST_SYNCED set to 1 whenever the event transitions from non-dirty to dirty.

remarks.para: If set to 1 this causes events on this calendar to be duplicated with Events#LAST_SYNCED set to 1 whenever the event transitions from non-dirty to dirty. The duplicated event will not be expanded in the instances table and will only show up in sync adapter queries of the events table. It will also be deleted when the originating event has its dirty flag cleared by the sync adapter.
Type: INTEGER (boolean)
